emptySegmentColor.description: Key of theme.colors or any valid CSS color value, by default the value is determined based on the color scheme value
emptySegmentColor.description_zh: key或任何有效的 CSS 颜色值，默认情况下该值是根据配色方案值确定的

fillDirection.description: Direction from which the circle is filled, 'left-to-right' by default
fillDirection.description_zh: 填充圆的方向，默认为“从左到右”

filledSegmentColor.description: Key of theme.colors or any valid CSS color value, theme.primaryColor by default
filledSegmentColor.description_zh: theme.colors 的键或任何有效的 CSS 颜色值，默认为 theme.primaryColor

labelPosition.description: Label position relative to the circle center, 'bottom' by default
labelPosition.description_zh: 标签位置相对于圆心，默认为 'bottom'

orientation.description: Orientation of the circle, 'up' by default

size.description: Diameter of the svg in px, 200 by default
size.description_zh: svg 的直径（以 px 为单位），默认为 200

thickness.description: Circle thickness in px, 12 by default
thickness.description_zh: 圆的粗细（以 px 为单位），默认为 12

transitionDuration.description: Transition duration of filled section styles changes in ms, 0 by default
transitionDuration.description_zh: 填充截面样式的过渡持续时间更改（以毫秒为单位），默认为 0
